    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >介绍</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1304470/extras/46f52b5023e489401586b1be549ef608.poster.avif?t=1712728345\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1304470/extras/46f52b5023e489401586b1be549ef608.webm?t=1712728345\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1304470/extras/46f52b5023e489401586b1be549ef608.mp4?t=1712728345\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>《降妖神兵》是一款以刷装备刷宝为核心玩法的古装单机游戏，并辅以经营元素如种菜、挖矿等，敌人和宝箱可以无限重置，打败boss获得不同品质的装备，从一无所有到战力巅峰，成为村民敬仰的大侠！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >玩法</h2><br>玩家可以在隐居处一边享受田园生活，一边修炼绝世武功；<br><br>通过种植蔬菜、池塘捕鱼、饲养家禽家畜等方式获取食材，烹饪出各种美食；<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1304470/extras/a1.JPG?t=1712728345\" /></span><br><br>在矿区采矿时不会有敌人干扰，可以安心采矿，升级武器装备；<br><br>本作战斗系统不需要太多的操作技巧，更适合休闲玩家；<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1304470/extras/f76a850c4356a9721d57400be71d25fa.avif?t=1712728345\" width=600 height=336 /></span><br><br>玩家可以邀请夫人加入队伍同行，提高战斗和挖矿等事件的效率；<br><br>打败妖王后，可以导入其他玩家的角色存档作为自己的协助者，共同战斗；<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1304470/extras/a2.JPG?t=1712728345\" /></span><br><br>回安全处睡觉，第二天地图就刷新，敌人和宝箱全部重置<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1304470/extras/fd5bdfc8f5515d15139cf7a167c16d2e.avif?t=1712728345\" width=600 height=336 /></span>",
